Products.title: Heritage Ring
Products.body_html:
An evolution of a classic. Subtle styling finds a new partner in fresh Scandinavian design. Heritage is available in four radiant colors: elegant silver, sleek black and confident stealth.

How to order:
1. Choose the color
2. Choose the ring size

If you don’t know your size, you can:
A. Order a free sizing kit by choosing “Send me a sizing kit”
B. Choose “I'll use another way to find out my size” and confirm your size later.
For more info:ouraring.com/sizing-instructions

SIZING KIT
You will receive the sizing kit before the ring so you can choose your size.
